				</h2> 
			</ContentBorderAnimated>
			<ul class="flex justify-center items-center gap-x-4 mt-10">
				<li>
					<Linkpill href="https://github.com/eduardoNBD" ><Github class="size-8"/>Github</Linkpill>
				</li>
				<li>
					<Linkpill href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/eduardo-e/" rel="noopener" target="_blank"><Linkedin class="size-8"/>Linkedin</Linkpill>
